# Cloudflare Pages — URL Rewrites
# Format: /short-url  /challenges/filename  200
# The 200 code = transparent rewrite (URL stays as /short-url in browser, great for iframes)
# Add a new line here for every new challenge you create in /challenges/

# Admin: do NOT add /admin → admin.html here for Workers static assets — it can cause
# redirect loops on *.workers.dev. Link to /admin.html from the site instead.
# (Cloudflare Pages at *.pages.dev can still use a Pages-only redirect rule in the dashboard if you want /admin.)

/lx-filesystem      /challenges/lx-filesystem       200
/lx-server-rescue   /challenges/lx-server-rescue     200
/lx-log-detective   /challenges/lx-log-detective     200
/lx-permissions     /challenges/lx-permissions       200
/lx-pipelines       /challenges/lx-pipelines         200
/lx-disk-space      /challenges/lx-disk-space        200

